articles.title: China is reportedly open to Elon Musk acquiring TikTok US - TechCrunch

articles.content: Chinese government officials have reportedly discussed a scenario where ByteDance sells TikTok’s United States arm to Elon Musk, should the Supreme Court uphold the law banning the app on January 19.… [+730 chars]
